'''Rho''' was a letter in the [[Tionese/Legends|Tionese alphabet]]. Rho was often used as a [[Callsign/Legends|call sign]] for [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Flight group/Legends|Flights]], specifically [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboats]]. Assault Gunboat designated ''Rho 3'' is one such example.

Rho was also used as an [[Engineer/Legends|engineering]] term.<ref name="RPG">[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game (first edition)|''Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game'']]</ref>

